  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t30%的壞貨率<br/>\n<br/>\r\n5個手機殼<br/>\r\n3條耳機綫 type-C x1 3.5mm x2<br/>\r\n兩個tws<br/>\n<br/>\r\n十件貨<br/>\n<br/>\r\n兩條有綫入耳式耳機，一個3.5mm，只有一邊有聲音，另一邊耳朵冇聲，另一個type-C耳機手機無法辨認到是耳機，完全沒聲音，都來自同一商戸<br/>\n<br/>\r\n有個藍牙耳機type-C充電位置整個脫出，昨天剛到貨開箱就發現無法充電，原來是因為這原因。另一個lightning接口充電的藍牙耳機暫時正常（才剛過24小時，將來會不會壞無法保證）<br/>\n<br/>\r\n早知道bt tws易壞，下單了purchased兩個，沒想到有一個就是壞的，估計整批貨都有問題<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS94VUZjZ3JXLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/xUFcgrW.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/xUFcgrW.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xUFcgrW.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9SMXg4VWVZLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/R1x8UeY.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/R1x8UeY.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/R1x8UeY.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9LZTRFNk9PLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ke4E6OO.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ke4E6OO.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ke4E6OO.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9xS2N5NjBoLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/qKcy60h.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/qKcy60h.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qKcy60h.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9kVTgxNHNJLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/dU814sI.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/dU814sI.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https